      <title>快速简单搭建博客</title>
      <link href="/2024/05/03/%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%BA%9F%E8%AF%9D%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
      <url>/2024/05/03/%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%BA%9F%E8%AF%9D%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安装博客环境"><a href="#安装博客环境" class="headerlink" title="安装博客环境"></a>安装博客环境</h2><h3 id="背景："><a href="#背景：" class="headerlink" title="背景："></a>背景：</h3><p>没有什么网页知识，也没有什么网页后端的知识，完全是想要有个个人的记录技术记录，给需要的人，和记录自己日子，自从三十以后，日子过得很快速很重复。</p><p>以前总是在CSDN上写文章。</p><p>有用的推荐，自己用开源免费</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># markdown 写作工具 ubuntu 下载appimage,直接运行就可以，注意下载属性改成可执行。</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># marktext</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#  两个快捷键盘 代码：ctrl+shift+k,表格：ctrl+shift+t</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 截图工具 Flameshot 火焰截图</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install flameshot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://img.sysgeek.cn/img/2023/07/flameshot-screenshot-tool-2.jpg" title alt="Flameshot 火焰截图工具" width="313"><h3 id="步骤："><a href="#步骤：" class="headerlink" title="步骤："></a>步骤：</h3><p>1、安装nodejs,也就是一个代码的运行环境。<mark>注意一定要用nvm安装，这是经验。</mark></p><p>2、安装matery主题</p><p><a href="matery%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98">https://github.com/blinkfox/hexo-theme-matery</a></p><p>3、免费部署到github pages</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 1、生成可以部署到github的博客文件</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 2、开启本地测试</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 3、自动部署到github pages</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 4、写文章</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo n <span class="string">&quot;文章名&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>部署的时候要配置，repo 注意写下图一样的</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:github用户名/github用户名.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img title src="file:///home/ubuntu/.config/marktext/images/2024-05-03-16-09-30-image.png" alt data-align="inline" width="523"><h3 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h3><p>目的就是快速搭建自己的网络自留地，花了两天时间，觉的这块理想情况下半个小时搞定，AI时代搭建个人免费的博客都这么慢，需要这些知识。这是我的一个目标，普通人可以快速实现自己网络博客。</p><blockquote><p><a class="link" href="https://stackedit.cn/">https://stackedit.cn/<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></p><p><a class="link" href="https://juejin.cn/post/7260486342898810939">MarkText使用教程 - 掘金<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
